Package javelin.model.world.place.guarded

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Academy
    Allows a player to learn one upgrade set.
    Dwelling
    Allows a player to recruit one type of unit.
    GuardedPlace
    A guarded place is a world feature that has a garrison army since the bieggining of the game.
    Guardian
    Single creature that guards an Item.
    Inn
    Allows a Squad to rest outside of a Town.
    Shrine
    Once it's garrison is defeated a priest will offer a wish to the heroes in return - a ScrollSpell (currently only obtainable this way) or map knowledge.
